	<h1>Welcome!</h1>
	<p>Hi, my name is Wei-Ming Liu, you can just call me Ben. I am glad you are reading my page. No matter how you came here, through a link, or by googling my name, Welcome!</p>
	<p>I am a <a href="http://www.cs.usc.edu/" target="_blank">USC (University of Southern California)</a> Computer Science M.S. student from Taiwan. I used to work as a chip designer in my country, but after several years of work I realized that I love coding. I hope one day I can work as a programmer. In order to gain more knowledge in this area, I started my study in USC.</p>
